Changing Tide CoGuild Leader<br><b>
"You must be the change you wish to see in the world." - Mahatma Ghandi</b></font></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualdarionshard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aldarion Shard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/3/01 12:51:20 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Anyone seen Hierophant Ixyl in Trak's Teeth?</span><hr size=1> &lt;&lt;Spirit of Cheetah is also something I wouldn't recommend as it is short duration and takes a valuable spell slot. Plus it overrides sow, so that when it fades you no longer have any speed boost. &gt;&gt;<br>
