Azeroeth Pax 45 Enchanter</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukatlynel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Katlynel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/3/01 1:07:38 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.asianavenue.com/indiegrrl/faedrake.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Anyone seen Hierophant Ixyl in Trak's Teeth?</span><hr size=1> OK people, let's say this one more time.<br>
IF A MOB IS AT 90% OF ITS HP LEVEL OR LESS, IT CAN SUMMON.  It will summon anyone who's aggroed it.<br>
It doesn't matter whether YOU do the damage or not.  If you haven't touched a mob but your tanks have, and you snare too soon, it will summon you. <p><font face="Verdana, Arial" size="2">
